defaultThe long term vision of the organi
defaultzation is to create a framework for a reconciliation process to be an integral part of any future political peace negotiations. Without reconciliation, we believe there can only be a ceasefire, and not a lasting peace.
defaultTo lay the groundwork for a lasting p
defaulteace, PCFF provides, first and foremost, the opportunity for Israelis and Palestinians to meet.
default&#xa0;
defaultIn the context of conflict, the two peoples remain alienated from one another, a separation which is fortified by feelings of fear, hatred, mistrust and dehuman
defaultization of the other.
default&#xa0;
defaultRather than allow bereavement to serve as yet another reason to hate, PCFF’s activities aim to use the personal stories of bereaved Israelis and Palestinians to prevent further bereavement on both sides, to demand a peaceful resolutio
defaultn to the conflict from 
defaultp
defaultolicymakers and to educate the public towards reconciliation.
